}}</ref><ref>{{книга|автор=Goodman, Michael.|заглавие=Contemporary literary censorship: the case history of Burroughs' Naked lunch|год=1981|издательство=|allpages=330|isbn=9780810813984}}</ref>.{{Врезка
 | Заголовок       = Пользовательские рейтинги<small>*</small>
 | Содержание      =
{{Рейтинг-5|4.5}} {{Не переведено 3|Shelfari|Shelfari|en|Shelfari}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shelfari.com/books/40158/Naked-Lunch|lang=en|title=Naked Lunch by William Burroughs|accessdate=11-07-2011|publisher=shelfari.com||archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/61JYH9fzc|archivedate=2011-08-30}}</ref>
<br />
{{Рейтинг-5|3.9}} [[amazon.com|Amazon]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/Naked-Lunch-William-S-Burroughs/product-reviews/0802119263/ref=dp_top_cm_cr_acr_txt?ie=UTF8&showViewpoints=1|lang=en|title=Customer Reviews: Naked Lunch|accessdate=11-07-2011|publisher=amazon.com||archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/61JYI7BDo|archivedate=2011-08-30}}</ref><br />
{{Рейтинг-5|3.8}} {{Не переведено 3|WeRead|WeRead|en|WeRead}}
<ref>{{cite web|url=http://weread.com/reviews/3499225883/Naked+Lunch./FBK-3499225883_-6?src=review|lang=en|title=Naked Lunch by William Burroughs|accessdate=11-07-2011|publisher=weread.com||archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/61JYIgFV3|archivedate=2011-08-30}}</ref>
